OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThousands call animal      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhelpline to give up pets   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An animal welfare charity says it has  
OL,6, received more than 4,000 calls from    
OL,7, people wanting to give up their pets.  
OL,9,FThe Scottish SPCA said the annual      
OL,10,Ffigure had tripled in a single year    
OL,11,Fsince 2021.                            
OL,13,FThe charity said it was down to the    
OL,14,Fcost of living crisis, with most       
OL,15,Fcallers to its helpline blaming        
OL,16,Ffinancial issues including vet bills.  
OL,18,FIt said some people were having to     
OL,19,Fchoose between feeding themselves or   
OL,20,Ftheir pets.                            
